{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":380,"text":"So the type of magic I like,\nand I'm a magician,"},{"time":3281,"text":"is magic that uses technology\nto create illusions."},{"time":7000,"text":"So I would like to show you\nsomething I've been working on."},{"time":9834,"text":"It's an application"},{"time":11105,"text":"that I think will be useful for artists --\nmultimedia artists in particular."},{"time":15772,"text":"It synchronizes videos\nacross multiple screens of mobile devices."},{"time":20161,"text":"I borrowed these three iPods\nfrom people here in the audience"},{"time":23106,"text":"to show you what I mean."},{"time":27776,"text":"And I'm going to use them to tell you\na little bit about my favorite subject:"},{"time":32468,"text":"deception."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36731,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":38776,"text":"One of my favorite magicians\nis Karl Germain."},{"time":43519,"text":"He had this wonderful trick\nwhere a rosebush would bloom"},{"time":48006,"text":"right in front of your eyes."},{"time":50442,"text":"But it was his production of a butterfly\nthat was the most beautiful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55717,"text":"(Recording) Announcer:\nLadies and gentlemen,"},{"time":58598,"text":"the creation of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":63000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":66715,"text":"Marco Tempest: When asked about deception,"},{"time":68957,"text":"he said this:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71960,"text":"Announcer: Magic\nis the only honest profession."},{"time":75451,"text":"A magician promises to deceive you --"},{"time":78108,"text":"and he does."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79518,"text":"MT: I like to think of myself\nas an honest magician."},{"time":83015,"text":"I use a lot of tricks,"},{"time":84726,"text":"which means that sometimes\nI have to lie to you."},{"time":89576,"text":"Now I feel bad about that."},{"time":92639,"text":"But people lie every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95140,"text":"(Ringing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":96188,"text":"Hold on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97225,"text":"Phone: Hey, where are you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":98904,"text":"MT: Stuck in traffic. I'll be there soon."},{"time":101997,"text":"You've all done it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103488,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105004,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106052,"text":"Right: I'll be ready\nin just a minute, darling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108425,"text":"Center: It's just what I've always wanted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111646,"text":"Left: You were great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113733,"text":"MT: Deception,"},{"time":115511,"text":"it's a fundamental part of life."},{"time":119248,"text":"Now polls show"},{"time":120677,"text":"that men tell twice\nas many lies as women --"},{"time":125000,"text":"assuming the women\nthey asked told the truth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127920,"text":"(Laughing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":129079,"text":"We deceive to gain advantage"},{"time":132000,"text":"and to hide our weaknesses."},{"time":135410,"text":"The Chinese general Sun Tzu said\nthat all war was based on deception."},{"time":141846,"text":"Oscar Wilde said\nthe same thing of romance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"Some people deceive"},{"time":148737,"text":"for money."},{"time":150284,"text":"Let's play a game."},{"time":153292,"text":"Three cards, three chances."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156610,"text":"Announcer: One five will get you 10,\n10 will get you 20."},{"time":159308,"text":"Now, where's the lady?"},{"time":161184,"text":"Where is the queen?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":163898,"text":"MT: This one?"},{"time":165488,"text":"Sorry. You lose."},{"time":167601,"text":"Well, I didn't deceive you."},{"time":170154,"text":"You deceived yourself."},{"time":173352,"text":"Self-deception."},{"time":175305,"text":"That's when we convince ourselves\nthat a lie is the truth."},{"time":179603,"text":"Sometimes it's hard to tell the two apart."},{"time":184905,"text":"Compulsive gamblers\nare experts at self-deception."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188495,"text":"(Slot machine)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190138,"text":"They believe they can win."},{"time":192630,"text":"They forget the times they lose."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195337,"text":"The brain is very good at forgetting."},{"time":198610,"text":"Bad experiences are quickly forgotten."},{"time":201816,"text":"Bad experiences quickly disappear."},{"time":206005,"text":"Which is why in this vast\nand lonely cosmos,"},{"time":208946,"text":"we are so wonderfully optimistic."},{"time":212930,"text":"Our self-deception\nbecomes a positive illusion --"},{"time":217061,"text":"why movies are able to take us\nonto extraordinary adventures;"},{"time":221814,"text":"why we believe Romeo\nwhen he says he loves Juliet;"},{"time":225616,"text":"and why single notes of music,"},{"time":228348,"text":"when played together,"},{"time":230690,"text":"become a sonata and conjure up meaning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234110,"text":"That's \"Clair De lune.\""},{"time":235552,"text":"Its composer, called Debussy,"},{"time":238193,"text":"said that art was\nthe greatest deception of all."},{"time":243100,"text":"Art is a deception\nthat creates real emotions --"},{"time":248348,"text":"a lie that creates a truth."},{"time":251967,"text":"And when you give yourself\nover to that deception,"},{"time":256172,"text":"it becomes magic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259473,"text":"[MAGIC]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":263596,"text":"(Music fades slowly)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":266278,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":278968,"text":"Thank you. Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281944,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}